snippet.title: Cosmopolitan UK
snippet.description:
Hi, welcome to Cosmopolitan UK’s YouTube channel! We’re your go-to for celebrity interviews, the latest on your favourite Netflix shows, K-Pop, Love Island, sex, royals and more! 

In our renowned series Beauty Lab, we get Cosmo's beauty editors to test and honestly review the latest makeup, skincare products and hair tools on camera. We also love getting the RuPaul’s Drag Race queens to shows us their epic makeup skills in our mesmerising video series, Cosmo Queens UK.

We also get A-List celebs on board to star in our video series like Spill The Tea, Up Close, Trials and Trivialations and Top of the Props. 

AND we publish videos every single week! Subscribe to Cosmo UK’s YouTube channel so you don’t miss out on our latest videos - you won't regret it.

#Beauty #LoveIsland #Makeup #Skincare #Haircare #KPop #CelebrityInterviews #Royals #CosmoQueensUK #BeautyLab
